channel.description:
ok.. this literally took me like.. half a second to write

go into 

com >> hotyute >> clientdata >> players >> Player.java

and under
[code]public class Player extends Entity {[/code]

add these....

[code]public void animation(int id) {
DataCollect.applyAnimationsUpdate(this, Short.parseShort(""+id), 0);
}
public void graphics(int id) {
DataCollect.applyGraphicsUpdate(this, Short.parseShort(""+id), 0);
}[/code]

now.. whenever you need to do an animation or a graphic update just do player.animation(ANIM ID); or player.graphics(GRAPHICSID);

simple.. good luck..

if u get an error make sure you impot the datacollect class like this
[code]import com.hotyute.clientdata.players.update.masks.*;[/code]


